author: Inside Edition
description: These selfies might not have been the best idea. In 2016,  Ben Innes took a selfie with a hijacker who claimed to be wearing a suicide belt while on a flight. In 2017, Kat Armendariz had a big smile on her face while her kid sister, Kimberly, was in agony during childbirth. In 2015, a dad-to-be snapped a selfie in the hospital delivery room while his wife, Sarah, was in pain giving birth. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: Selfies Taken In Inopportune Situations

author: Inside Edition
description: Stella the dog knows when it's fall. Autumn is definitely her favorite season. Every year, Stella bolts out of the house leaping right into a gigantic pile of leaves in the front yard. Stella began her leaps of joy when she was just a puppy racing to the leaves at her home in Freeport, Maine. Videos show her looking happy and wagging her tail with her head buried in the leaves. Inside Edition spoke to Stella's owner, Jody Hartman.
title: Fall Is Stella The Dog's Favorite Season
